      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, powered by the iconic 2JZ-GTE twin-turbocharged inline-six mated to a Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. This A80 retains its factory sequential turbochargers, exhibiting no boost leaks and strong spool characteristics. The Torsen limited-slip differential remains tight, ensuring optimal torque distribution to the rear wheels. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive timing belt service and new cam seals. The double-wishbone suspension setup provides precise handling, though the bushings show age appropriate for its driver-status. While the aesthetic reflects its history as a driven machine, the compression numbers are healthy and the drivetrain is robust. A mechanically honest example of Japanese grand touring excellence.",
